data.description: *Conveniently Located Between Routes 19 & 79 Providing Easy Access to Donaldson's Crossroads, Waterdam Plaza, Shops, Restaurants, Medical, South Pointe, Meadows Racetrack & Casino, Tanger Outlets, & More!* This well cared for 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome offers a spacious center island eat-in kitchen, sun-drencheed living room, spacious dining room, large master bedroom suite & full bath, finished game room, rear deck featuring a retractable awning providing 360 degree hilltop views, a private wooded rear yard, & 2 car garage. Enjoy low maintenance living, community sidewalks, close school bus stop, home warranty included!
data.whatILove: Only 1 mile from Donaldsons Crossroads and 1 mile to 79 and Southpointe. The bar and stools are included. I may also leave the washer and dryer. The refrigerator is brand new. The kitchen, powder room and spare bedroom just painted. The front door, shutters and trim just painted. Mulching and drive way sealing is scheduled for this summer. Sprinkler system in every room was just inspected. HOA includes snow removal from common drives and sidewalks, mulching and drive sealing every other year.  School bus stop is just at the intersection and there are sidewalks. Great location and great neighborhood!
